Maïwenn https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ma%C3%AFwenn 0 Maïwenn (sometimes credited as Maïwenn Besco or her birth name Maïwenn Le Besco, French: [maj.wɛn lə bɛs.ko]; born 17 April 1976) is a French actress, film director and screenwriter.
